## рҹ“– Overview

**TrustBridge** is a self-contained, modular communication tool designed to operate entirely over a LAN without requiring internet connectivity. It enables secure, encrypted text messaging and file sharing within an organization's internal network.

### рҹҢҗ Network Independence
- **100% LAN-based** - No internet required
- Works offline on local network
- No external cloud servers or APIs
- All communication stays within your network

---

## рҹҡҖ Features

### Core Features
- вң… **Zero Trust Architecture** - Every request authenticated and authorized
- вң… **AES-GCM Encryption** - All messages and files encrypted end-to-end
- вң… **LAN Independence** - Works completely offline, no internet needed
- вң… **Real-time Chat** - Instant messaging with Socket.io
- вң… **File Sharing** - WhatsApp-like file sharing with encryption
- вң… **Multiple File Selection** - Select and send multiple files at once
- вң… **Any File Type Support** - Images, videos, documents, executables, etc.
- вң… **Offline Message Delivery** - Messages delivered when user comes online
- вң… **Unread Message Count** - Green badge like WhatsApp
- вң… **5 Role-Based Access Control** - Admin, Super User, Team Lead, Team Manager, Team Member

### User Roles & Permissions

| Role | Description | Permissions |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| **Admin** | System Administrator | Full system management, user creation, view logs |
| **Super User** | Company Owner | Receives updates, communicates with Leads/Managers |
| **Team Lead** | Department Manager | Manages team, chats with team members |
| **Team Manager** | Sub-manager | Manages team members |
| **Team Member** | Standard User | Basic chat and file sharing |

